Content: I'm going to tell the scaryest story you will ever here in your life. So i was at a cookout with my family. My cousin Jim said he needed to use the bathroom _so we excused Jim from the table and allowed him to go. However_ 5 min after Jim had already gone in the house we all heard screaming coming from the bathroom window. So me aunt Shila and my brother Phil went to go check up on him. We asked if he was alright in there 5 times but no answer. By now the screaming had stopped and we were getting worried so I kicked the door down only to see the the toilet gone Jim gone and one turd on the ground with a note next to it that read _"i have seen the light and i flew to it'. To this day I have always been afraid of the bathroom. rip uncle Jim.
